   558	### 5. Skill Installation Command And Agent-Specific Paths
   559	
   560	Normative claims:
   561	
   562	- `rhei install-skills` usage accepts `--agent <NAME>`, `--local`, `--link`,
   563	  `--uninstall`, `--dry-run`, and `--skills <LIST>`.
   564	- Supported agents are `claude-code`, `cursor`, `windsurf`, `copilot`,
   565	  `kilocode`, `pi`, `codex`, `antigravity`, and `all`; `all` expands to every
   566	  concrete agent.
   567	- Default skill list is
   568	  `rhei-plan-writer,rhei-plan-worker,rhei-state-machine-writer`.
   569	- Global and local paths are agent-specific:
   570	  - Claude Code: `~/.claude/skills/rhei-<skill>/` and `~/.claude/CLAUDE.md`;
   571	    local `.claude/skills/rhei-<skill>/` and `.claude/CLAUDE.md`.
   572	  - Cursor: `~/.cursor/rules/rhei-<skill>.mdc`; local
   573	    `.cursor/rules/rhei-<skill>.mdc`.
   574	  - Windsurf: `~/.windsurfrules` or
   575	    `~/.codeium/windsurf/memories/global_rules.md`; local `.windsurfrules`.
   576	  - Copilot: `~/.github/copilot-instructions.md`; local
   577	    `.github/copilot-instructions.md`.
   578	  - Kilocode: `~/.kilocode/rules/rhei-<skill>.md`; local equivalent.
   579	  - Pi: `~/.pi/rules/rhei-<skill>.md`; local equivalent.
   580	  - Codex: `~/.agents/skills/rhei-<skill>/SKILL.md`; local
   581	    `.agents/skills/rhei-<skill>/SKILL.md`; no registration file.
   582	  - Antigravity: `~/.antigravity/rules/rhei-<skill>.md`; local equivalent.
   583	- Claude registration uses a `# rhei` block with skill paths and triggers.
   584	- Cursor files use `.mdc` frontmatter and embed `SKILL.md` content.
   585	- Windsurf and Copilot use marker-delimited markdown sections.
   586	- Kilocode, Pi, and Antigravity use plain markdown rule files.
   587	- Codex uses standard skill directories and discovers local/global skills
   588	  without marker registration.
   589	- Local installation finds a project root by walking up for common markers and
   590	  falls back to `cwd`; local symlinks are relative.
   591	- Re-running installation removes/replaces existing Rhei skill files and
   592	  refreshes them.
   593	- Skill sources resolve relative to the installed binary
   594	  `../share/rhei/skills/` or repo dev fallback `skills/`.
   595	- `--link` symlinks; default copies.
   596	- `--dry-run` prints planned actions and does not write.
   597	- `--uninstall` removes copied/symlinked skill files and registration blocks.
