    20	- **missing-validation**: The spec requires `by_type` keys and override `type` values to be declared non-root node kinds and override `level` values to fit the plan structure. State-machine loading validates only empty/reserved `by_type` keys and undefined profiles; override level/type are not represented. Evidence: `docs/specs/rhei-states.spec.md:812`; `docs/specs/rhei-states.spec.md:817`; `crates/rhei-validator/src/lib.rs:1113`; `crates/rhei-validator/src/lib.rs:1142`.
