    25	
    26	- **missing-validation**: State `description` is required by the transition and writer specs, but `StateDef.description` is optional and explicitly permissive. Evidence: `docs/specs/rhei-transitions.spec.md:571`; `docs/specs/rhei-state-machine-writer.spec.md:70`; `crates/rhei-validator/src/lib.rs:478`.
