    32	
    33	- **implementation-diverges**: Manual transition execution does not reject transitions from final states before applying exact or wildcard rules. The transition spec says final states are absorbing and wildcard transitions do not match final states. Evidence: `docs/specs/rhei-transitions.spec.md:766`; `crates/rhei-cli/src/main.rs:5060`.
