    35	- **no-discrepancy**: Ready-task discovery skips terminal and gating states, so `rhei run`/callback scheduling and automatic ready selection avoid autonomous work from gating states. Evidence: `crates/rhei-cli/src/main.rs:8670`; `crates/rhei-cli/src/main.rs:8692`; `crates/rhei-cli/src/main.rs:8437`.
