   170	## SY-003: Task Metadata Fields
   171	
   172	### SY-003-A: Required state and metadata ordering diagnostics exist
   173	
   174	Classification: `no-discrepancy`
   175	
   176	The parser requires every parsed task to have `**State:**`, rejects `**Prior:**` or `**Assignee:**` before state, rejects metadata after task content, and reports malformed near-miss metadata lines as parse diagnostics. Evidence:
