   234	
   235	### SY-004-A: Automatic state-machine lookup and auto-discovered name checks match the spec
   236	
   237	Classification: `no-discrepancy`
   238	
   239	When no override path is supplied, the CLI resolves sibling `states.yaml` for single-file plans and workspace-root `states.yaml` for workspaces, checks the YAML `name` against `**States:**`, and falls back to the built-in `rhei` machine only when the plan declares `rhei`. Evidence:
