   321	### SY-005-B: Duplicate prior references are not checked
   322	
   323	Classification: `missing-validation`
   324	
   325	The spec forbids duplicate references in one `**Prior:**` list. The validator iterates dependencies for existence and ancestor checks but does not track a per-task seen set for duplicate prior ids. Evidence:
