   355	```
   356	
   357	## Missing Information Handling
   358	
   359	If required input is missing:
   360	
   361	- Ask the user to supply workflow intent, parameter surface, and state-machine scope.
   362	- Do not invent parameters to cover uncertain parts of the workflow.
   363	- If the template would be a thin wrapper over a single plan with no real parameterization, push back: `rhei-plan-writer` is the better tool.
   364	- If the workflow needs more than roughly ten inputs or more than one state machine, push back: consider splitting into separate templates.

